			<p class="TableBody" data-label="†Table_Body" data-name="†Table_Body" data-split="d1e1471" style="text-align:center;mso-fareast-font-family:minorEastAsia"><span data-bkmark="para10053_1999335927"></span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:8pt">Height</span><span data-bkmark="para10053_1999335927"></span></p>
