<p class="ParaInd" data-label="†Para_Ind" data-name="†Para_Ind" data-split="d1e1602" style="mso-style-name: !msorm;text-indent:24pt;"><span data-bkmark="para10067_1999335927"></span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">The aerodynamic configuration of the airdrop-capable folding-wing </span><span data-bkmark="BMABBRE100155"></span><span data-bkmark="BMSPELLING100158"></span><span class="allcaps" data-name="allcaps" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt">UAV</span><span data-bkmark="BMSPELLING100158"></span><span data-bkmark="BMABBRE100155"></span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman"> is depicted in </span><a class="citationfigure" data-alias="FigureRef" data-id="2090138879" href="pone.0343305.xhtml#f1"><span class="FigureCitation" data-name="FigureCitation"><span class="Figure" data-alias="Figure" data-id="320196436"><span data-bkmark="BMHYPHEN100157"></span><span class="FigXref" data-name="‡FigXref" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt">Fig</span></span><span class="FigXref" data-name="‡FigXref" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt"> </span><span data-bkmark="BMHYPHEN100157"></span><span data-alias="SeqNo" data-id="793890933"><span class="FigXref" data-name="‡FigXref" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt">1</span></span></span></a><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">. When the </span><span data-bkmark="BMABBRE100156"></span><span data-bkmark="BMSPELLING100159"></span><span class="allcaps" data-name="allcaps" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt">UAV</span><span data-bkmark="BMSPELLING100159"></span><span data-bkmark="BMABBRE100156"></span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman"> decelerates to a safe deployment speed threshold via the parachute system, the torsion spring mechanism triggers release, applying equal-magnitude complementary torques to both wings for smooth and controlled deployment.</span><span data-bkmark="para10067_1999335927"></span></p>

<figure>
<figcaption class="FigureCaption" data-alias="FigureCaption" data-id="ran15385" data-label="†Figure_Caption" data-name="†Figure_Caption" data-split="uni446771" id="f1"><span data-bkmark="para10068_1999335927"></span><span class="Figure" data-alias="Figure" data-id="1148765842"><span data-bold="REMOVE" data-proid="100162" data-prorange="proStart"></span><span class="figurenumber" data-name="‡figure_number" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5pt"><b>Fig</b></span></span><span class="figurenumber" data-name="‡figure_number" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5pt"><b> </b></span><span data-alias="SeqNo" data-id="1319292224"><span class="figurenumber" data-name="‡figure_number" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5pt"><b>1</b></span></span><span class="figurenumber" data-name="‡figure_number" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5pt"><b>.</b></span><b><span style="font-family:Times New Roman"> </span></b><span class="figuretext" data-name="‡figure_text" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5pt"><b>Airdrop-capable </b></span><span data-bkmark="BMABBRE100160"></span><span data-bkmark="BMSPELLING100164"></span><span class="figuretext" data-name="‡figure_text" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5pt"><b>UAV</b></span><span data-bkmark="BMSPELLING100164"></span><span data-bkmark="BMABBRE100160"></span><span class="figuretext" data-name="‡figure_text" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5pt"><b> </b></span><span class="msoDel"><del cite="mailto:Auto Process" class="ice-del ice-cts" data-changedata="" data-cid="26" data-last-change-time="1771911417824" data-time="1771911417824" data-userid="" data-username="Auto Process" datetime="1771911417824"><span class="figuretext" data-name="‡figure_text" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5pt"><b>Modeling</b></span></del></span><span class="msoIns"><ins cite="mailto:Auto Process" class="ice-ins ice-cts" data-changedata="" data-cid="27" data-last-change-time="1771911417824" data-time="1771911417824" data-userid="" data-username="Auto Process" datetime="1771911417824"><span class="figuretext" data-name="‡figure_text" style="font-family:Times New Roman; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5pt"><b>Modeling.</b></span></ins></span><span data-bkmark="para10068_1999335927"></span></figcaption>
